Project: Agentic Website Learning & Autonomous QA System

Goal:
Build an AI agent that logs into a web application and automatically learns the entire website.

Features:
- Planner Agent
- ReAct Execution Agent
- Browser Tools (Playwright)
- DOM Summarizer
- Interactive Element Detection
- Navigation Graph Builder
- Vector Memory (RAG)
- UI Fingerprinting
- Exploration Engine (BFS + DFS hybrid)
- Page State Detection
- Automatic Test Case Generator
- Self-Healing Selectors

Agent workflow:
Login → Crawl menus → Explore pages → Build navigation graph → Store UI fingerprints → Generate test cases → Execute automation.

Architecture:
Planner → ReAct Agent → Browser Tools → DOM Observer → Memory (Vector DB + Graph) → Exploration Engine → Test Generator.

Goal is to build a real autonomous QA automation agent.